No. 10-6465. Melody Ramsey, Petitioner v. Eric K. Shinseki, Secretary of Veterans Affairs. 562 U.S. 979, 131 S. Ct. 433,

178 L. Ed. 2d 319,

2010 U.S. LEXIS 8185. October 18, 2010.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Same case below, 364 Fed. Appx. 432.
